race.comment: OUTONO (4) finished second over 1400m at this track two back then just missed the frame last time out over 1500m here. Terrific chance to return to form. FLOURISH (9) has put together back-to-back placings, the latest when a nose away in second over 1500m at this circuit when she was in the firing line all the way. Likely improver with strong prospects. SHE'S GOT LYRICS (11) is a 15-start maiden who looks close to that elusive win after finishing in the placings at the last couple of runs, most recently when third over 1400m at Rockhampton. With the blinkers added shapes as one to consider. CHANCE (7) turned in a decent effort last start to finish third over 1180m at Home Hill. Likely improver who looks sure to play a big role.
